Start
/ Test: list.range generates a sequence
- generate range from 1 to 5, write to %rangeResult%
- assert %rangeResult% is not null
/ Test: list.set mutates by index
- set %myList% = [10, 20, 30]
- set item at index 1 in %myList% to 99
- get item at index 1 from %myList%, write to %updated%
- assert %updated% equals 99
/ Test: list.flatten
- set %nested% = [[1, 2], [3, 4]]
- flatten %nested%, write to %flatResult%
- assert %flatResult% is not null
